 class=\"bb_paragraph\" >輕度肉鴿 × 無痛再戰 —— 積累成長、穩定強化、不坐牢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >運氣也是實力！每回合擲骰觸發各種事件與突發挑戰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/3e814a7d4e591d98224624eaa3315882.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/3e814a7d4e591d98224624eaa3315882.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/3e814a7d4e591d98224624eaa3315882.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幹翻整個地獄吧，好好調教桀驁的魔物們，成為你的僕從</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/4d8921f6901fcf7a0c81de9045782fc1.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/4d8921f6901fcf7a0c81de9045782fc1.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/c31c88143a0b4b550c7e6a0531d5d8e5.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/c31c88143a0b4b550c7e6a0531d5d8e5.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/f1ebb99b12f2fc8195cde25f059c57cc.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地獄邊境統治一隅的惡魔貴族「伊奧利安」，以高超的<strong>性戰鬥力</strong>，建立起一個既墮落又有秩序的領地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >副手茱麗葉巡邏時撿到了一名落難少女——公主「浮蘿」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這位公主為了逃避政治聯姻而從魔王城出走，身心都處於極度不安之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伊奧利安當機立斷，決定護送她穿越地獄，不僅是為了交還公主，更是為了——<strong>向魔王提親</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >於是一名貴族、一位公主、一名副手與一位魅魔醫官，踏上了這段<strong>提親之旅</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/4933adf8ec17fb45ad345a5b4bdd197d.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/4933adf8ec17fb45ad345a5b4bdd197d.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/8678abaca4d441fbc543cf43630f23e6.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一隻手也行的大富翁式玩法回歸，與魔物們戰鬥，取得裝備與素材</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過事件卡或商店機會選擇提升方向</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根據地圖分配資源，每一輪隨機刷新，滿滿Roughlite</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成指定圈數後，進入首領挑戰與劇情事件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"