ight=878 /></span></p>", "short_description": "這是一款結合擲骰戰鬥與戀愛喜劇的成人視覺小說。主角伊奧利安為了地獄公主「浮蘿」，率領夥伴踏上十八層試煉，擊敗各種怪物與守門人，最後闖入深淵魔王城與浮蘿的母親——傲慢強勢的魔王陛下——正面對決。一路上，玩家將見證隊伍的情感糾葛、笑料百出的對話，以及逐漸揭露的魔王過往。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 繁體中文, 法文, 義大利文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 俄文, 土耳其文, 波蘭文, 泰文, 荷蘭文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 葡萄牙文 - 葡萄牙, 西班牙文 - 拉丁美洲, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/981926e56c03f38eaf0bc237842c3b0ff40c41a5/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1771939577", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/01eda0a12e6633db2badfbe0402fba6bcc6c499f/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1771939577", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/01eda0a12e6633db2badfbe0402fba6bcc6c499f/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1771939577", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["WorkNite Games"], "publishers": ["Alice Publication", "Eternal Alice Media"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 26800, "final": 26800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 268"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "2", "description": "策略"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 2 月 9 日"}}}}, "us": {"3907210": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Married Into Hell", "steam_appid": 3907210, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4347020, 4347060], "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/8710970ba385eacdb7375d1ee9d1dd61.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/1d279b496adfa7b5c76ee88cbd15feca.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/1d279b496adfa7b5c76ee88cbd15feca.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/1d279b496adfa7b5c76ee88cbd15feca.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% Equipment Drop Rate!</strong> <br>Be on time for some steamy fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/077f50ea08e5f43734183f70de83f959.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/077f50ea08e5f43734183f70de83f959.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/077f50ea08e5f43734183f70de83f959.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer  hell and seduce every demoness commander you meet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light Roguelite × Zero Frustration</strong> — Grow stronger with every run. Permanent upgrades, stable progress, and no jail time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Luck Is Power!</strong> <br>Roll the dice each turn to trigger random events and unexpected challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eba3356e0142811d5dd4816741d425e5.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eba3356e0142811d5dd4816741d425e5.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eba3356e0142811d5dd4816741d425e5.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer the entire hell and train the defiant monsters well — make them your loyal servants</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/4d8921f6901fcf7a0c81de9045782fc1.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/4d8921f6901fcf7a0c81de9045782fc1.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/c31c88143a0b4b550c7e6a0531d5d8e5.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/c31c88143a0b4b550c7e6a0531d5d8e5.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eecf2e66827ece3ead3c222a3a499484.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are <strong>Aeolian</strong>, a decadent demon noble ruling a remote corner of Hell. Through your... <i>“charisma”</i>, you've created a land both orderly and depraved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, your trusty aide <strong>Juliet</strong> finds a runaway girl—none other than <strong>Flow</strong>, the Demon King’s daughter, fleeing a political marriage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With quick (and horny) thinking, you vow to escort her across the 18 layers of Hell—not just to return her, but to <strong>propose</strong> to the Demon King!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/4933adf8ec17fb45ad345a5b4bdd197d.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/4933adf8ec17fb45ad345a5b4bdd197d.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/550a6af26611fa3441243f25bf1af8eb.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The classic <strong>one-hand-friendly board-game style</strong> returns!<br>Battle fierce monsters to collect powerful <strong>gear and materials</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>event cards</strong> or <strong>shop encounters</strong> to choose your growth path.<br>Distribute your resources wisely across the map — every round brings a <strong>freshly randomized Roguelike experience</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After completing a set number of laps, you’ll unlock <strong>boss battles</strong> and <strong>special story events!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/bd27f0d50088b8f3b655278c659571e9.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/b49e869554c4858f0aa9201e4a362aea.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/b4c7513315f5dd1c7bb8ade0b62c4c3a.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.