0/extras/1d279b496adfa7b5c76ee88cbd15feca.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/1d279b496adfa7b5c76ee88cbd15feca.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/1d279b496adfa7b5c76ee88cbd15feca.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% Equipment Drop Rate!</strong> <br>Be on time for some steamy fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/077f50ea08e5f43734183f70de83f959.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/077f50ea08e5f43734183f70de83f959.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/077f50ea08e5f43734183f70de83f959.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer  hell and seduce every demoness commander you meet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light Roguelite × Zero Frustration</strong> — Grow stronger with every run. Permanent upgrades, stable progress, and no jail time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Luck Is Power!</strong> <br>Roll the dice each turn to trigger random events and unexpected challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eba3356e0142811d5dd4816741d425e5.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eba3356e0142811d5dd4816741d425e5.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eba3356e0142811d5dd4816741d425e5.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer the entire hell and train the defiant monsters well — make them your loyal servants</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/4d8921f6901fcf7a0c81de9045782fc1.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/4d8921f6901fcf7a0c81de9045782fc1.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/c31c88143a0b4b550c7e6a0531d5d8e5.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/c31c88143a0b4b550c7e6a0531d5d8e5.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/eecf2e66827ece3ead3c222a3a499484.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are <strong>Aeolian</strong>, a decadent demon noble ruling a remote corner of Hell. Through your... <i>“charisma”</i>, you've created a land both orderly and depraved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, your trusty aide <strong>Juliet</strong> finds a runaway girl—none other than <strong>Flow</strong>, the Demon King’s daughter, fleeing a political marriage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With quick (and horny) thinking, you vow to escort her across the 18 layers of Hell—not just to return her, but to <strong>propose</strong> to the Demon King!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/4933adf8ec17fb45ad345a5b4bdd197d.avif?t=1771939577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras_big/4933adf8ec17fb45ad345a5b4bdd197d.webp?t=1771939577 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/550a6af26611fa3441243f25bf1af8eb.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The classic <strong>one-hand-friendly board-game style</strong> returns!<br>Battle fierce monsters to collect powerful <strong>gear and materials</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>event cards</strong> or <strong>shop encounters</strong> to choose your growth path.<br>Distribute your resources wisely across the map — every round brings a <strong>freshly randomized Roguelike experience</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After completing a set number of laps, you’ll unlock <strong>boss battles</strong> and <strong>special story events!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.poster.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.webm?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/de25d7da71dbd17251f1fb6c6ac74126.mp4?t=1771939577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/bd27f0d50088b8f3b655278c659571e9.avif?t=1771939577\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/b49e869554c4858f0aa9201e4a362aea.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/b4c7513315f5dd1c7bb8ade0b62c4c3a.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/4f05a68b787db26534b549dd97ce72bb.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/885e2c96281c57bfd77dd267c6a20343.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/e9e38e718b60ba4ad0017b9720c1ec24.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3907210/extras/310e57f439e43caea0d8b8280ea45471.avif?t=1771939577\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_im